list.abstract: Third（英 [θɜːd]，美 [θɜːrd]），英语单词，词性是数词、名词、形容词、副词。作数词时译为第三；作名词时译为三号；作形容词时译为第三的；作副词时译为第三（点）。 Third的复数是thirds。短语搭配有third party（第三方）、a third（三分之一）等。近义词有tertius、ternary。例句有“Third, they now dominate left-of-centre politics.”（第三，他们目前在偏左派的政治力量中占主导地位。）
third ，1998年11月24日出生于泰国，是kamikaze公司FZ组合一员 泰国男歌手、演员。就读于朱拉隆功大学 发行了单曲《Reminder》 和《 Just One Word》。

yingyinNormal.en: And third, it's not news, it's well-established.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第三，这不是新事，这是公认的事实。

yingyinNormal.en: You are the third call tonight. Really?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这已是今晚的第三件。真的？

yingyinNormal.en: We lost the third baby, Jack. I'm very sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们失去了第三个孩子，杰克。我很遗憾。

yingyinNormal.en: A third plant is then cut to mimic an attack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再模拟被动物食用来剪第三株阿拉伯芥。

yingyinNormal.en: And the third reason: Stan has a small wiener.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有第三个原因，斯坦的弟弟超小。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, it's third down. No it's not, it's second.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喂，是第三次十码进攻了。才不是，这是第二次而已。

yingyinNormal.en: Triplets. Speaking of, you know where our third is?
yingyinNormal.zh: 三胞胎啊。说到这个，第三只去哪儿了？

yingyinNormal.en: For most guys that's like a third or fourth date kinda thing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对其他男人来说，那是第三、四次约会才做的事。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, he was discovered by a neighbor in the final third of tubercular meningitis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，他结核性脑膜炎第三末期时被邻居发现。

yingyinNormal.en: And you can search one door and one room and another door and another room and the third door the third room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以点击这一扇门进入这个房间，也可以点另一扇门进另一个房间，或者第三扇门和房间。

yingyinNormal.en: And I'd like to start with the third part first, if it's cool, unless, that would be confusing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我先从第三部分说起，希望不会令你觉得混淆。

yingyinNormal.en: Third one we've lost. We're burning them behind the blocks. Burning them. That's what it's come to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我们失去的第三个人了，我们在牢区后面火化了他们，火化了，他们只能这样了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not going anywhere until you tell me what's going on. I'd sit on your bed, but that's your third "never."
yingyinNormal.zh: 除非你告诉我原因，否则我哪儿也不去。我本来想坐你的床，但那是你的第三"绝"。

yingyinNormal.en: Third, the bathroom schedule. Now, I'm given to understand women have different needs, so, we'll have to discuss that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第三，厕所使用时间表，我了解到女人对厕所的用法有所不同，所以我们应该讨论一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Quit feeling sorry for yourself. All right? That can start right now. Wake the hell up. And, you know... the... what was the third thing?
yingyinNormal.zh: 别再自怨自艾。行了吗？马上就可以开始。振作起来。还有第三是什么事来着？

yingyinNormal.en: Third of all, he's actually pretty funny. But fourthly, now that I know him, I would say I actually do wanna be friends with Auggie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第三，他其实挺好玩儿的。但是第四，现在我了解他了，我真的想和奥吉做朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: Third, we know how to fight this disease. We know the protocols. And we know that when they're followed, they work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第三，我们知道该如何应对这一疾病，我们知道这些方案，我们知道当我们遵循这些方案时，他们能够起到作用。

yingyinNormal.en: The third time of what, Jack? Third slow. Everything went sideways, and then it stopped, then I jumped.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么第三次，杰克？第三次减速，一切都倒向一边，然后就停下了，我就跳下来了。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, well, what's the third option? That I have coitus with her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，第三个选项是什么？我跟她交媾。

yingyinNormal.en: When the third moon rises, he must fly. If he lives, he's the one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当月亮第三次升起，他必须能飞起来，如果他能平安回来，他就是预言之子。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Last year marked the <highlight>third</highlight> year in a row of when Indonesia's bleak rate of deforestation has slowed in pace.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 去年是印度尼西亚森林砍伐速度连续放缓的第三年。

examination_example.sentence: Indonesia has the <highlight>third</highlight>-largest area of tropical forest in the world and one of the highest deforestation rates.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 印度尼西亚是世界上热带森林面积第三大的国家，也是森林砍伐率最高的国家之一。

examination_example.sentence: In order to increase sales, they should create a "<highlight>third</highlight> stepping stone" between infant wear and older kids' clothes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了促进销售额，他们应该在婴儿服装和大龄儿童服装之间创造“第三过渡阶段”。

examination_example.sentence: At the start of this century, about one-<highlight>third</highlight> of crop workers were over the age of 35.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 本世纪初，大约三分之一的农作物工人年龄超过35岁。

examination_example.sentence: About a <highlight>third</highlight> say the problem of fake news lies in "misinterpretation or exaggeration of actual news" via social media.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 约三分之一的人表示，假新闻的问题在于通过社交媒体“误解或夸大真实新闻”。

examination_example.sentence: Students who do not need the extra training could cut their debt mountain by a <highlight>third</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不需要额外培训的学生可以减少三分之一的债务。

examination_example.sentence: And <highlight>third</highlight>, through a more diffuse "halo effect," whereby its good deeds earn it greater consideration from consumers and others.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 第三，通过更广泛的“光环效应”，它的善行赢得了消费者和其他人更多的关注。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Third</highlight>, the use of paper checks gives consumers several days of "float".
examination_example.sentence_trans: 第三，使用纸质支票给消费者提供了几天的浮动期。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Third</highlight>, they now dominate left-of-centre politics.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 第三，他们目前在偏左派的政治力量中占主导地位。

sense_info_list.en: each of three equal parts into which something is or may be divided

examination_example.sentence: Consider that nearly two-<highlight>thirds</highlight> of students will experience the "ninth-grade shock," which refers to a dramatic drop in a student's academic performance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 考虑一下，将近三分之二的学生会经历“九年级休克”，这是指学生的学习成绩急剧下降。

examination_example.sentence: Nearly two-<highlight>thirds</highlight> of us grab fast food once a week, and we get almost 25% of our daily calories from snacks.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们中近三分之二的人每周吃一次快餐，我们每天几乎25%的热量来自零食。

examination_example.sentence: Many of us grow up believing that skipping breakfast is a serious mistake, even if only two <highlight>thirds</highlight> of adults in the UK eat breakfast regularly, according to the British Dietetic Association, and around three-quarters of Americans.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 即使我们很多人从小就认为，不吃早餐是一个严重的错误，但是根据英国饮食协会的统计，英国只有三分之二的成年人经常吃早餐，美国人约有四分之三。

sense_info_list.en: constituting number three in a sequence

examination_example.sentence: I started a <highlight>third</highlight> drawer for these big discoveries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我为这些重大发现设立了第三个抽屉。

examination_example.sentence: When Sandra Day O'Connor finished <highlight>third</highlight> in her class at Stanford Law School, she could not find work at a law firm.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当Sandra Day O'Connor在斯坦福法学院以班级第三的成绩毕业时，她没能在一家律师事务所找到工作。

examination_example.sentence: As a <highlight>third</highlight> generation native of Brownsville, Texas, Mildred Garza never pleased move away.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为得克萨斯州布朗斯维尔的第三代土生土长的人，Mildred Garza从不愿意搬走。

examination_example.sentence: Of those Australians who still have a landline, a <highlight>third</highlight> concede that it's not really necessary.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在那些仍有固定电话的澳大利亚人中，三分之一的人承认这并不是真的必要。

examination_example.sentence: Globally, a <highlight>third</highlight> of Sumatran cubs in zoos don't make it to adulthood, so I decided to give them round-the-clock care at home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在全球范围内，动物园里有三分之一的苏门答腊幼虎无法活到成年，所以我决定在家里全天候照料它们。
